A4.text: Snow Patrol released their fifth studio album, A Hundred Million Suns, in 2008; their sixth, Fallen Empires, in 2011; their seventh, Wildness, in 2018; and their eighth, The Forest Is the Path, in 2024.

A7.text: Under the Iron Sea is the second studio album by the English rock band Keane, released on 12 June 2006.
